Package: trendkit
Type: Package
Title: Time Series Trend and Anomaly Detection
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Guy", "Schvitz",
      email = "guy.schvitz@ec.europa.eu",
      role = c("aut", "cre"),
      comment = c(ORCID = "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-5036-4123")
    )
  )
Description: This package provides a set functions for detecting trends, 
    anomalies, and patterns in time series data. It includes methods for 
    deviation-based detection, percentile analysis, surge identification, 
    trend analysis, and local maxima detection. Designed for analysing 
    event counts, monitoring metrics, and identifying outliers in temporal 
    data.
